OL,7,FProfessor Jimmy Choo now runs the JCA
OL,8,FLondon Fashion Academy in the heart of
OL,9,FMayfair. His aim is to pass on his
OL,10,Fskills to the next generation of
OL,11,Fdesigners.
OL,13,FThe Academy takes on approximately 150
OL,14,Fstudents and teaches diploma, bachelor
OL,15,Fand masters degrees.
OL,17,FProfessor Choo said: "Where's the best
OL,18,Feducation? Still London.
