OL,7,FPerry Davidson's collection closed the
OL,8,Fnight. He took inspiration from
OL,9,Fmilitary clothing and designers such
OL,10,Fas Stone Island.
OL,12,FHis brand P3RRY DAVIDS8N focuses on
OL,13,Fachieving zero waste in both the
OL,14,Fcreative and production processes,
OL,15,Futilising military surplus, recycled
OL,16,Fmaterials, and deadstock fabrics.
